{"tid":2175323,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"一個90後香港出世無BNO既社工手足發起聯署","createTime":"2020-08-26T11:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T23:51:14.000Z","uid":51080,"like":73,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4b190900a02246a1eac3c6e348c47c6aec4806","tid":2175323,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"請廣傳 Please share!<br />\n<br />\n本人係94年香港出世無BNO既社工手足發起聯署!<br />\n<br />\n以下聯署既主要對象:<br />\n1. 1997年6月30日或之前香港出世無BNO: <br />\n90-97年 (90後) 香港出世既抗爭者果陣年紀好細，全家冇BNO、佢地冇幫我地申請BNO，果陣年紀好細對社會認知同政治認知不足，所以我地請求英國重開BNO申請;<br />\n<br />\n2. 1997年7月1日或之後香港出世:<br />\n由於有唔少抗爭者都係1997年7月1日或之後 (97至00後: 18-23歲) 無BNO，英國收唔曬香港手足真香港人; 5眼聯盟早前起Twitter表示考慮提供救生艇比97之後既香港人，所以透過聯署支持5眼聯盟拯救我地; <br />\n<br />\n3. 持有BNO既香港人;<br />\n<br />\n越多手足香港人簽名聯署能容易說服到英國人同更多英國議員支持方案。5眼聯盟同時會回應我地訴求； 詳細聯署內容請登入先睇到，唔該🙏🙏🙏<br />\n<br />\n聯署link: <a href=\"https://t.co/NOBptSAeOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNOBptSAeOg&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=300b5c3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/NOBptSAeOg</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署結束後將會交比全部英國議員MPs同5眼聯盟外長。<br />\n<br />\n#齊上齊落 #煲底見 #香港人加油"},{"pid":"170664ab2863e4eb2a2640687a8410a9912ef99e","tid":2175323,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:50:27.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"ff3e7ababe03b320039114126972a583e3250fa8","tid":2175323,"uid":51080,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"其中一位英國議員嘅回覆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaWKUGS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaWKUGS.jpg&h=8f14efbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"714d0635b49ef061fae56c8de633776bbcf38c56","tid":2175323,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係英國冇留非BNO嘅出世紙底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi